---
layout: false
title: Blog | Rafael Scalp Artist
permalink: /blog/
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es-AR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Blog | Rafael Scalp Artist — Micropigmentación Capilar</title>
<meta name="description" content="Artículos sobre micropigmentación capilar, calvicie, cuidados y todo lo que necesitás saber. Por Rafael Oropeza, especialista en SMP en Buenos Aires.">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; background: #000; color: #fff; line-height: 1.6; }
  :root { --verde: #57C84D; }

  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif; font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #fff; text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-back { font-size: 13px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); text-decoration: none; }
  .nav-back:hover { color: #fff; }

  .blog-hero {
    padding: 140px 24px 64px;
    max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  .blog-tag {
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--verde);
    margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;
  }
  .blog-tag::before { content: '— '; }
  .blog-title {
    font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif; font-weight: 900;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .blog-subtitle { font-size: 17px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }

  .blog-grid {
    max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 24px 96px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
  }
  .blog-empty {
    max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 64px 24px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .post-card {
    background: #0d0d0d;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden;
    text-decoration: none; color: #fff;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }
  .post-card:hover { border-color: rgba(87,200,77,0.3); }
  .post-card-img {
    width: 100%; aspect-ratio: 16/9;
    object-fit: cover; display: block;
    background: #1a1a1a;
  }
  .post-card-body { padding: 24px; flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .post-card-date {
    font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .post-card-title {
    font-family: 'Arial Black', sans-serif; font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .post-card-desc {
    font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    line-height: 1.6; flex: 1; margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .post-card-link {
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--verde);
  }

  footer {
    padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }
  footer a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); text-decoration: none; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="/" class="nav-logo">Rafael Scalp Artist</a>
  <a href="/" class="nav-back">← Volver al sitio</a>
</nav>

<div class="blog-hero">
  <span class="blog-tag">Blog</span>
  <h1 class="blog-title">Todo sobre micropigmentación capilar</h1>
  <p class="blog-subtitle">Artículos, guías y respuestas para que llegues informado a tu consulta.</p>
</div>

{% set posts = collections.posts %}
{% if posts.length > 0 %}
<div class="blog-grid">
  {% for post in posts %}
  <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-card">
    {% if post.data.image %}
    <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" class="post-card-img">
    {% else %}
    <div class="post-card-img"></div>
    {% endif %}
    <div class="post-card-body">
      <div class="post-card-date">{{ post.date | fechaCorta }}</div>
      <div class="post-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</div>
      {% if post.data.description %}
      <div class="post-card-desc">{{ post.data.description }}</div>
      {% endif %}
      <div class="post-card-link">Leer artículo →</div>
    </div>
  </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
{% else %}
<div class="blog-empty">Próximamente — los primeros artículos están en camino.</div>
{% endif %}

<footer>
  <a href="/">Rafael Scalp Artist</a> · Micropigmentación Capilar en Buenos Aires
</footer>

</body>
</html>
